INSERT INTO admin_post_page VALUES("1","about","About Nethaat","About Nethaat","About Nethaat","About Nethaat","<span style=\"font-size: small\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\">Nethaat</span> is an interactive online market place on the web to get buyers,sellers and admirers of arts,crafts and designer items,gather together to interact.<br />  <br />  About the name : Haat is a central place in a village/town where both buyers and seller meet to buy and sell household and hand made products.This place is always full of activity . The haat attracts buyer for better price as well as available options of many sources .For a seller the availability of a common place with varied buyers is a best place to be in.This unique experience has been transformed on the nethaat.<br />  <br />  It has always been seen that <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong>artisans</strong></span> with magnificient ability to create crafts of exquisite workmanship would create the craft and would go for selling thier items in make shift places.After end of the show they are gone with no access of their products by buyers and admirers.This urge to have a common place for Artisans,Artists and Designers to be globally accessible created nethaat.<br />  <br />  <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong>Artists</strong></span> have always followed their inner voice and dedication to create many exclusive arts in various forms like paintings,sculpture and much more to inspire others.<br />  <strong><br />  </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong>Designers</strong> </span>have always been regarded by all of us to take our fashion to next century in any form in clothing,jewellery,accessories etc.They, with their ever changing and evolution in designs ,colors and trends have changed the way we look at fashion.<br />  <br />  During the development of the project ,it was also felt that many of us have inner creativity in the field of arts,crafts,dresses etc.but the creativity were compromised due to demand of other priorities in life.This enthusiasm is being regenerated in the <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong>Homemaker</strong></span> category.<br />  <br />  So in whichever category you fit in just open your store yourself in easiest steps on nethaat to showcase and sell it to the world.<br />  <br />  We thank all for their support to this initiative.<br />  <br />  The following unique features of nethaat are being introduced for an ultimate surfing and interactive experience.<br />  <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Comic Sans MS\">HAATING</span></strong></span><br />  Our shopping experience doesn&#39; t complete, till we have done a bit of negotiation.So get a taste of online negotiation experience with haating.For haating ,login to use this innovative feature.<br />  <br />  <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Comic Sans MS\"><strong>WORKSHOP</strong></span></span><strong><br />  </strong>It is a place where the buyer can get the handmade items custom made as per his requirement from the the seller of his choice<br />  <br />  <span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Comic Sans MS\">LOCKER</span></strong></span><strong><br />  </strong><span style=\"font-size: small\">This is a secured place for a seller to keep their designs and handcreated stuffs in itand can showcase or sell only to the buyer or the people of his choice by sending the password. </span></span>  <p><span style=\"font-family: Comic Sans MS\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\">REMINDER</span></strong></span><br />  <span style=\"font-size: small\">Its a module where we can set the reminder for any important event like birthdays ,anniversarys etc and get the reminders with ability to send the message ,gifts or gift certificates for the occassion.<br />  <br />  So let&#39;s together as a community ,experience this unique online experience.</span></p>  <!--Session data--><!--Session data--><!--Session data--><!--Session data--> <!--Session data-->","2011-03-07 23:22:31");
