INSERT INTO admin_post_page VALUES("3","faq","Frequently Asked Questions","Frequently Asked Questions","Frequently Asked Questions","Frequently Asked Questions","<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,255)\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span class=\"mainHD\">Frequently Asked Questions</span></span></strong></span><br />  <br />  (1).Nethaat is an online market place for the sellers and buyers of hand made products from across the globe. Any one who creates handmade products can register and start selling in minutes and buyers get choice of various items from the globe.<br />  <br />  (2). Is it required for us to register at nethaat? Though you may browse the portal without registering, it is recommended to register in order to effectively use unique interactive features of the platform and make use of all the modules in my .<br />  <br />  (3).All the online shops on the platform have their own Handmade products,terms,condition and the payment is made directly into sellers Paypal account.<br />  <br />  As a seller give importance to fulfilling the reqirements of the buyer ,serve them the best to attract maximum customer satisfaction.<br />  <br />  As a buyer your valuable feedback to the sellers response and fulfilment of the order will help rate the seller.This rating will encourage the sellers and help buyers to learn about the sellers credibility.<br />  <br />  (4). Buyer may contact the seller through the internal messaging system to know more about the product ,shipping,details before placing the order<br />  <br />  &nbsp;<br />  <br />  .<!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" type=\"hidden\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" type=\"hidden\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" type=\"hidden\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" type=\"hidden\