INSERT INTO tbl_ticket_messages VALUES("5","8","0","Thanks for contacting us.Following are the clarifications.  (1).As a member you can in a basic account upload items in 25 space provided for free in your nethaat store.  (2)Upload 1 item per space with option to have total 5 photos for each item.  (3)Display the product worn by some one or a dummy to give a feel to the product.  (4)Mention the price in USD and this will be converted automatically in to Rs in india ,japanese yen in japan etc.    In the selling price .Please include the price of Paypal charges (Look for the paypal fees at https://www.paypal.com/in/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_display-fees-outside) and Nethaat charges of 3.5%   (5).Payment goes directly in to your own paypal account.You just need a email address to create the paypal account.Pl wait for the announcement for the details shortly.    (6).Please mention about the shipping destination.If you wish to ship to india put india additionally if you want to ship to USA select usa etc and define the shipping price.This chrges defined will be paid by buyer to you.    (7).After you get paid ,ship your product.Now you get an invoice from nethaat for a charges of 3.5% to pay.     Hope your doubts are cleared.Any further queries pl get back to us mentioning the ticket on this mail for a quicker response.    Thanks    Nethaat Team","2010-12-07 00:00:00");
INSERT INTO tbl_ticket_messages VALUES("6","9","0","Hello Mr Rohit,    Thanks for contacting  us.    We aplolgize for the inconvinience .All the prices are to be mentioned in USD by seller themselves.Since we do not have access to your login ,due to privacy.you will have to do it your self.     Pl go to my item list in your login and you can edit in very easy steps.    In case of any problem,pl let us know.Pl use the same ticket id for any doubts related to this enquiry.    Thanks    Customer support  Nethaat team","2010-12-09 00:00:00");
INSERT INTO tbl_ticket_messages VALUES("7","10","0","Hello Mr.Vicky,    Thanks for the message.Pinky had spoken to you and hope your queries have been answered.    For getting more clicks  and conversion to sales,  please note that upload 1 item on  evry page with maximum 5 pics in different angles/styles for buyer to get a clear and aclearer view ,as if he was buying the item physically.Please put the cloth being used ,color guarantee ,size etc to make the specifications clear.    Also if we can dress the items to dummy,worn by some one witout showing the face of the person wearing it,will give a feel to the product.    Hope You will follow the simple rules to sell on line in order to attract maximum traffic to your shop and inturn convert the clicks to order.    Thanks    Nethaat Team","2010-12-10 00:00:00");
INSERT INTO tbl_ticket_messages VALUES("8","12","0","Dear Mr Amit,  Thanks for your interest in nethaat.    Please follow the following steps in order to register and open your online store in minutes.    (1).Click on &#39;open a store&#39;  (2).Fill in all the fields and sign up.In user name ,Please use a unique name which goes with your store/items.  (3).You will be sent an confirmation email to the email id you registered with.  (4).Pl click on the link to authenticate.  (5).Fill up the remaining fields on the form displayed upon authentication.  (6).Please put your paypal id for the payment to be directed directly to your account.If you do not have a paypal account ,you can open with your email id within minutes.Please check for paypal fees at this link    https://www.paypal.com/in/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_display-fees-outside   (7).In your account pl go thru each modules.  (8).You can start uploading your store by clicking on &#39;sell my item&#39; and you can edit any item in &#39;my item list&#39;.Please fill in all the fields ,upload photos ,define country where you want to ship ,define the shipping rates etc.  (9).Upon uploading ,you will see the item in the new item list on home page.      In Basic account you get 25 space in your store for free ,where you can upload your 25 handmade items.You can delete the old items and add new items in this space provided.Nethaat sends an service invoice @3.5% after you have sold your item and payment goes directly into your account.    When your business grows,you may upscale further.See for the details  in purchase package.    In case of any difficulty ,kindly get back to us with the same ticket number for us to act faster.    We welcome to the nethaat community !Happy selling.    Regards    Nethaat Team","2010-12-27 00:00:00");
