INSERT INTO tbl_ticket_messages VALUES("27","41","0","Hello Don,    Thanks for the message.Following are the fee structure being charged at nethaat from the sellers.    a).Basic    Artisans = 3.50%  Artists = 3.50%  Designers = 3.50%  Homemakers = 3.50%    0-25 Items  (Open your online shop and get space for 25 items for free.Rotate your items in this space of 25 items.Nethaat sends you an invoice @ rate metioned against the category of the item price ,after any product has been sold.When your store grows upgrade to Master or Masterpro with fixed fees and no commissions.)       b).   Master (26-100 item space)      1 Month   USD 10.00       6 Months   USD 48.00         12 Months   USD  84.00     (Pay only fixed fees with no commissions.)        c).  Master Pro  (101-500 item space)        1 Month   USD 14.00       6 Months   USD 68.00         12 Months   USD  118.00      (Pay only fixed fees with no commissions.)        The above fee info can be found in the sellers login at Purchase Package,    We will shortly display the details on the site for public.    In basic account you dont pay as long as your item is not sold and there is no fixed charges.    You can always upgrade to a higher model with more space and features with a fixed cost and no commission as per details given below.    Hope above is clear.Please let us know if you need further clarifications.    Regards    Nethaat team","2011-04-28 00:00:00");
