ese units work in coordination with different subsidiaries of Shilpi Handicrafts ( Shilpi ,Prakhya, Weave N Prints, Pugmarks and Shilpi Sansthan) which are dealing in fabrics, handicrafts, garments and accessories, gifts etc. The company is currently venturing into retailing and service sector and thus holds its promise of promoting crafts and craftsperson","1","durga","","","","","","3","1","2010-11-21 21:16:28","0","0","","","0","","","","1","","","","0","0");
