INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("2","1","2009-12-09 17:19:15","2009-12-10 01:19:15","Nethaat  is an ecommerce place on web to get buyers, sellers and admirers of arts ,crafts and designers together on an unique platform.INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("19","1","2010-05-27 14:58:44","2010-05-27 22:58:44","This is an example of a WordPress page, you could edit this to put information about yourself or your site so readers know where you are coming from. You can create as many pages like this one or sub-pages as you like and manage all of your content inside of WordPress.INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("21","1","2010-05-30 15:06:28","2010-05-30 23:06:28","Nethaat  is an ecommerce place on web to get buyers, sellers and admirers of arts ,crafts and designers together on an unique platform.INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("20","1","2010-05-30 14:07:47","2010-05-30 22:07:47","Nethaat  is an ecommerce place on web to get buyers, sellers and admirers of arts ,crafts and designers together on an unique platform.INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES("13","1","2010-07-14 01:16:53","2010-07-14 09:16:53","Nethaat  is an ecommerce place on web to get buyers, sellers and admirers of arts ,crafts and designers together on an unique platform.\n\nIt has been always seen that Artisans ,who with their magnificent ability to create crafts for centuries of exquisite workmanship would make the craft and would go places to makeshift places to sell them and make them popular.After end of one show they are gone with no access to their products by the buyers and  admirers.The idea to create a permanent place of  all  Artisans,Artist and designers  to be accessible globally created nethaat.\n\nArtist have always followed their inner voice to create many exclusive art in various forms like painting,sculptures and much more to inspire others.\n\nDesigners have always been regarded by all of us to take us forward to the next century fashion in any form in clothing,jewelery,accessories etc .They have with their ever changing and evolution in designs and trend have changed  the way we look at the fashion .\n\nWhile discussing the development of the project ,it was also felt that many of us  had an inner creativity in ourselves for creating  handmade items may be its arts, crafts, dresses ,but gradually buried  down due to demand of other priorities in life and no market to cater to.This enthusiasm is being regenerated in the homemaker category.\n\nSo, in what ever field just open your e store yourself  in the easiest way on nethaat  , showcase  and sell it to the world !\n\nYour comments to this creativity initiative are welcome.\n\nWe thank all for their support.\n\n<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" />\n\n<!--Session data-->\n<input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /> <input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" />\n\n<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" />","About nethaat","","inherit","open","open","","2-autosave","","","2010-07-14 01:16:53","2010-07-14 09:16:53","","2","http://www.seologistics.com/nethaat/blog/?p=13","0","revision","","0");
