lot of practice and once you are on you\'ll become better and better with time. Once you\'ve had a little practice you\'ll have the most extensive shoe wardrobe of anyone you know.\n\nWith this level of creativity your shoes can transform into customized, engaging compliments to your personality. You can also turn a pair of cheap pumps or flats into refined accessories for you ensembles, so you should learn to decorate your plain shoes to get the great look you desire. The next time you\'re considering a new pair of shoes thinks instead of redecorating a pair you already own and impress your friends with your creativity.","Getting creative with your old shoes","","inherit","open","open","","103-revision-7","","","2011-02-20 14:33:54","2011-02-20 14:33:54","","103","http://www.nethaat.com/blog/?p=129","0","revision","","0");
